data.description: This full brick home is within minutes of Fort Stewart, shopping schools and all things Hinesville has to offer. Located on a quiet cul-de-sac  with very little traffic. this home offers 3 bedroomd and 2 1/2 baths with a formal living and dinning room, den with fireplace and eat in  kitchen. Master Bedroom has a full bath and nice sized walk in closet. The property has been used as a rental for the past five years. Great property to  add to an investment portfolio.
